OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fsunny and very warm into this evening
OL,7,Fwith temperatures only slowly falling
OL,8,Faway after dark. Clear skies
OL,9,Fcontinuing overnight and staying
OL,10,Frather warm, making it quite
OL,11,Funcomfortable for sleeping.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FTemperatures rapidly rising
OL,14,Fin the strong sunshine and becoming
OL,15,Fexceptionally hot inland by the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Very localised
OL,17,Fthunderstorms may develop later.
OL,18,FCooler on many coasts with sea breezes
OL,19,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
