OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FBreezier on Wednesday and slightly
OL,7,Fless hot, with rather strong easterly
OL,8,Fwinds in places. Remaining very warm
OL,9,Fon Thursday and Friday with a small
OL,10,Fchance of showers and perhaps
OL,11,Fthunderstorms.
